room_title: Escape room "The Hangover" by Bent Key Escape in Effingham
room_description: It is your best friend’s bachelor(ette) party and you’re in the Fabulous Las Vegas, Nevada.  After a great night out full of partying, you all wake up the following morning not remembering anything.  The only thing you do know is you were all passing around a camera capturing all the memories.  You need to find the camera before your secrets are exposed in 1 hour.
